  "text": "Effect of temperature on larvicida activity: taking into account the temperatures average in Cuba [CITATION_1] Chlorine treatment: The FP was treated with sodium dichloroisocyanurate resulting in chlorine concentration of 2.25mg/L, pH 6.0 and incubated at 25 \u00b0C for 24h.",
